    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Mesiotelus iranicus sp. n., female.A habitus, dorsal view; B intact epigyne, ventral view; C vulva, dorsal view; D macerated epigyne, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.2 mm, unless stated otherwise.Abbreviations: Ah—anterior hood, Cd—copulatory duct, Co—copulatory opening, Fe—fenestra, Fo—fovea, Re—receptacle." ;
